<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.2.7">
<l>peṇṭir vāḻvār niṉ ṉop pāraip peṟutu meṉṉu mācai yālē</l>
<l>kaṇṭa varkaḷ pōkko ḻintār kaṇṇi ṇaiyāṟ kalakka nōkki</l>
<l>vaṇṭu lāmpūṅ kuḻali ṉāruṉ vāya muta muṇṇa vēṇṭik</l>
<l>koṇṭu pōvāṉ vantu niṉṟār kōvin tānī mulaiyu ṇāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The women who live to watch [you] with desire,</l>
<l rend="indent">saying “Let us obtain one like you,”</l>
<l>watching with bewilderment, with both eyes, they do no leave.</l>
<l>Ladies with locks [full of] blossoms where bees wander,</l>
<l rend="indent">Wanting to drink the nectar of your lips,</l>
<l>Come and stand [here] to reach and take [you].</l>
<l rend="indent">Govinda! You [should] drink from [my] breast.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
